@Timo1993 
That error code conveys one of two possible issues. One would be that the device does not contain a decoder that has codec profiles matching the one needed to decode the video file. The other would be that the decoder does indeed have a matching profile, but does not contain levels that can handle the codec level required by the video file.

Would you be able to provide a link to the mp4 file that is reproducing this issue?

